query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 1 AND q.score <= 10
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('angular2-template',
'cakephp-2.0',
'erb',
'ironpython',
'jboss7.x',
'jekyll',
'lua-table',
'powerpoint',
'react-navigation',
'reshape',
'ubuntu-16.04');
